-- Stocks Recoup Early Losses Leaving FTSE 100 Index Little Changed in London
-- B y   A d a m   H a i g h
-- 2012-01-27T10:07:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-27/stocks-recoup-early-losses-leaving-ftse-100-index-little-changed-in-london.html
U.K. stocks recouped losses, leaving
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed. The gauge slid 0.1
percent to 5,791.72 as of 10:05 a.m. in  London , having earlier
fallen as much as 0.8 percent.  The FTSE 100 is heading for a gain of 1.1 percent this
week.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
